node.text:
Some extra red suit pics since the last post hit over 1 million likes😵‍💫🤯

When I used to play Among Us, I always picked the red character and eventually my community wanted to see me in a red suit! I promised I would do a photoshoot about 8 months ago lol.. I guess you could say this is an ode to that era❤️ so many people discovered my channel during that time, I met many incredible friends and hit my all time viewership high of 150,000.. I’ll never forget how crazy it all was! I’m so grateful for the opportunity to entertain with videogames for a living.. forever thankful for the support and love you all have consistently shown me the past few years☺️❤️
